name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Wildee search & rescue for animal lovers

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Wildee generate income from your daily web browsing and use it to help animals.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Setting Wildee as your search engine, you will make a better world for all the living species endangered and the left behind animals in rescues. 

Our search engine powered by Google will generate incomes from ads and commercials. Wildee will redistribute it to animal rescues, animal missions and make sure each animal is treated fairly.

As Gandhi said, “The greatness of a nation can be judged by the way its animals are treated.”
